{
  "page": "Smallfolk (TV)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the common people, see <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">Smallfolk</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(248, 233, 208);border:none;\">\"Smallfolk\"</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size: 100%\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:right;\">Season 2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">&#160;—&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;text-align:left;\">Episode 6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"HOTD Smallfolk.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/14/HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg/300px-HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"170\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/14/HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg/450px-HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/14/HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg/600px-HOTD_Smallfolk.jpg 2x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Original air date</th><td>\nJuly 21, 2024</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Running time</th><td>\n66 minutes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Credits</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Directed by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrij_Parekh\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Andrij Parekh\">Andrij Parekh</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Written by</th><td class=\"plainlist\">\nEileen Shim</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">Episode chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\">\n<tbody><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">←&#160;Previous</th>\n<th style=\"width:50%;text-align:center;\">Next&#160;→</th>\n</tr><tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/Regent_(TV)\" title=\"Regent (TV)\">Regent</a>\"</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\"<a href=\"/index.php/The_Red_Sowing_(TV)\" title=\"The Red Sowing (TV)\">The Red Sowing</a>\"</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#f8e9d0;border:none;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_House_of_the_Dragon_episodes\" title=\"List of House of the Dragon episodes\">List of episodes</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>\"<b>Smallfolk</b>\" is the sixth episode of <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_2\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 2\">season two</a> of the HBO <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/medieval_fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:medieval fantasy\">medieval fantasy</a> television series <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>. Running 66 minutes long, it premiered on July 21, 2024. The episode was written by Eileen Shim and directed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrij_Parekh\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Andrij Parekh\">Andrij Parekh</a>. Music was composed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramin_Djawadi\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ramin Djawadi\">Ramin Djawadi</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Official_synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Official synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Plot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Plot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Cast\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cast</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Starring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Starring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Co-starring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Co-starring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Uncredited\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Uncredited</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Reception\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reception</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Official_synopsis\">Official synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Official synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With few options left, Rhaenyra summons a trusted knight for a risky venture and plots with Mysaria to catalyze the smallfolk. Meanwhile, Daemon's unease grows, and Aemond takes steps to reshape the Green Council.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Plot\">Plot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Plot\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Differences_between_Fire_%26_Blood_and_House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"Differences between Fire &amp; Blood and House of the Dragon\">Differences between Fire &amp; Blood and House of the Dragon</a></div>\n<p><i>To be added</i>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cast\">Cast</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Cast\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Starring\">Starring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Starring\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matt_Smith\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Matt Smith\">Matt Smith</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emma_D%27Arcy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Emma D&#39;Arcy\">Emma D'Arcy</a> as Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olivia_Cooke\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Olivia Cooke\">Olivia Cooke</a> as Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alicent_Hightower\" title=\"Alicent Hightower\">Alicent Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Toussaint\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Steve Toussaint\">Steve Toussaint</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fabien_Frankel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fabien Frankel\">Fabien Frankel</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matthew_Needham\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Matthew Needham\">Matthew Needham</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Larys_Strong\" title=\"Larys Strong\">Larys Strong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sonoya_Mizuno\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sonoya Mizuno\">Sonoya Mizuno</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Mysaria\" title=\"Mysaria\">Mysaria</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Glynn-Carney\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tom Glynn-Carney\">Tom Glynn-Carney</a> as King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ewan_Mitchell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ewan Mitchell\">Ewan Mitchell</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phia_Saban\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Phia Saban\">Phia Saban</a> as Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Helaena_Targaryen\" title=\"Helaena Targaryen\">Helaena Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Collett\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Harry Collett\">Harry Collett</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jacaerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Jacaerys Velaryon\">Jacaerys Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoebe_Campbell\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Phoebe Campbell\">Phoebe Campbell</a> as Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Daemon)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jefferson_Hall_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jefferson Hall (actor)\">Jefferson Hall</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tyland_Lannister\" title=\"Tyland Lannister\">Tyland Lannister</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freddie_Fox_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Freddie Fox (actor)\">Freddie Fox</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gwayne_Hightower\" title=\"Gwayne Hightower\">Gwayne Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gayle_Rankin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Gayle Rankin\">Gayle Rankin</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abubakar_Salim\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Abubakar Salim\">Abubakar Salim</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn of Hull</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinton_Liberty\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Clinton Liberty\">Clinton Liberty</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Velaryon\" title=\"Addam Velaryon\">Addam of Hull</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kurt_Egyiawan\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kurt Egyiawan\">Kurt Egyiawan</a> as Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Orwyle\" title=\"Orwyle\">Orwyle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kieran_Bew\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Kieran Bew\">Kieran Bew</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellora_Torchia\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ellora Torchia\">Ellora Torchia</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Kat\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kat\">Kat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Bennett_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Tom Bennett (actor)\">Tom Bennett</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Ulf_White\" title=\"Ulf White\">Ulf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_Russell_Beale\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Simon Russell Beale\">Simon Russell Beale</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Strong\" title=\"Simon Strong\">Simon Strong</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Co-starring\">Co-starring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Co-starring\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sian_Brooke\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Sian Brooke\">Siân Brooke</a> as Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Aemma_Arryn\" title=\"Aemma Arryn\">Aemma Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Paul_Kennedy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paul Kennedy\">Paul Kennedy</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jasper_Wylde\" title=\"Jasper Wylde\">Jasper Wylde</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Flanagan\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Anthony Flanagan\">Anthony Flanagan</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Darklyn\" title=\"Steffon Darklyn\">Steffon Darklyn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicholas_Jones_(actor)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Nicholas Jones (actor)\">Nicholas Jones</a> as Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Bartimos_Celtigar\" title=\"Bartimos Celtigar\">Bartimos Celtigar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phil_Daniels\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Phil Daniels\">Phil Daniels</a> as Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/inde