>Tok Stephen</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Waters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eddard Waters\">Eddard Waters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebecca_Calder\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Rebecca Calder\">Rebecca Calder</a> as a Harrenhal servant</li>\n<li>Kieron Jecchinis as a Dragonstone Elder</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clive_Brunt\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Clive Brunt\">Clive Brunt</a> as TBA</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Graeme_McKnight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Graeme McKnight\">Graeme McKnight</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Paxter_Strong\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paxter Strong\">Paxter Strong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Paul_Valentine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paul Valentine\">Paul Valentine</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Germund_Strong\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Germund Strong\">Germund Strong</a></li>\n<li>Tom Clegg as a Kingslander</li>\n<li>Jack Staddon as TBA</li>\n<li>Erica Ford as a handmaid</li>\n<li>Erwan Sion as a clam digger</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oscar_Eskinazi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Oscar Eskinazi\">Oscar Eskinazi</a> as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Velaryon\" title=\"Joffrey Velaryon\">Joffrey Velaryon</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Uncredited\">Uncredited</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Smallfolk_(TV)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Uncredited\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paddy_Considine\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Paddy Considine\">Paddy Considine</a> as King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reception\">Reception</span><span class=\"mw-edits